    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it literally looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and there\u2019s not a single scratch or dent to be found. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, this is it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
