    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating applied; there are zero stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinct new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and every interior surface\u2014from the dashboard to the original floor mats\u2014is immaculate. Mechanically, the vehicle is indistinguishable from new, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at the authorized dealership with every service documented. The engine bay is pristine, the transmission shifts with factory precision, and the tires retain over 90% of their original tread. Included are both original keys, all owner manuals, and a comprehensive folder of service receipts. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been treated as a prized possession rather than a daily driver.",
      "price": 43850.0,
